The album was released on June 27, 2011 as part of Queen's 40th Anniversary. Deep Cuts Volume 2 was released simultaneously as the second five reissues of the Queen studio albums (News of the World, Jazz, The Game, Flash Gordon and Hot Space). All the songs are sampled from these five albums.
